ai-mil3.5.9:1.2_0: “A bull elephant knows that it arises from a royal bull elephant.”
ai-mil3.5.9:1.3_0: “Great king, anyone who knows he is angry, he who thinks: ‘I’ll be reborn’?”
ai-mil3.5.9:2.2_0: “A farmer, great king, who was a farmer, put on the earth in earth and understands the gods of rainy season, and who knows that it will be reborn.”
ai-mil3.5.9:2.4_0: “In the same way, great king, anyone who knows: ‘I will be given up.’”
ai-mil3.5.9:4.1_0: ninth enquiry is the ninth enquiry.
